{"id": "pos051", "name": "Cam_Dash_702_11_17", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma... Aroma, wake up.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Umm... Sister? ... Mr. Asakura's car...?\n......! Where are we going!?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "N...... NO! Are you taking me to the lab...? I heard the conversation between you two. I'm not going!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "N, no, it's not what you think! Calm down first!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... I previously don't know what I'm supposed to do. However, seeing this reaction from you... I'm relieved.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I'm taking you to \"JOEZ Cafe\" to meet up with NEKO.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Eh!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I got in contact with her. She informed me about the many things that had happened since you left... Need to return the car to them as well.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sister...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Don't call me that.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "No... Sorry. My emotions are kinda messed up right now...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Since you heard our conversation, then it should be easier for you to understand what I'm about to tell you.\nRight now, I... can't treat you as simply my little sister.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "The tone of your speech, your expressions... Compared to what they were before you ran away, I feel even more strongly about this now.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It doesn't mean that you're not my little sister. It's that this body... doesn't belong solely to Aroma. The more I grew conscious of this, the more I didn't know what I should do...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I understand.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Because I have the same feeling as well... After I left you guys, those memories that don't belong to me became clearer and clearer... At first, they were still just some blurry, confusing images that felt very dated. But now... even the dream I just had felt as if it was something that just happened yesterday.  \n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Is that so...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I... want to know who \"the other me\" is.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Looks like I made the right decision. Thank... good... ness...... Eh?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sister...?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Haha... Am I crying? I just felt like a weight was lifted off my chest...yet...I feel some sort of sadness...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I always... always knew... that the real you was already gone that night... But once I admitted this, I had no idea what kind of feelings, or what identity I should take on when facing the current you... Even when you call me \"sister\", it just sounds so... unfamiliar... I... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... (Places hand on Helena)\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Not calling you sister, that's... I can't do that. Our memories, and the years we spent together after I woke up, they didn't disappear... You are my older sister.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "No matter how many \"me\"s exist in this body; no matter where I go next, what happens afterward; no matter... whether you're able to treat me as your little sister or not... you will always be my sister. The sister I love more than anyone else in this world. So... please don't say something like that...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "Parks car"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<i>*Sobs*... *Bawls*...</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma、起きて。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ぅ…ん……お姉ちゃん？……朝倉さんの車……？\n……！どこに行くの！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "いや……イヤ！また私を実験室に連れて行くの……？\n2人の会話は聞いてた！私イヤ！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ち、違うわ！落ち着いて！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……私もどうするべきか分からなかった。\nでも、今の反応を見て確信したわ。\n私の判断は間違ってなかったって。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "今から、あなたを「JOEZ Cafe」に連れて行く。\nそこでNEKOと落ち合うの。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "えっ！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あの子には連絡しておいたわ。\n私たちが離れていた間のことも聞いた……この車も持ち主に返さないといけないでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "そんな風に私を呼ばないで。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "いいえ……ごめんなさい。\nそうじゃないの。\nちょっと、感情がぐちゃぐちゃで……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "私たちの会話を聞いていたんでしょう？\nなら、分かってくれるはず。\n今の私は……あなたを単純に自分の妹として見ることができない。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなたの話し方、目……離れ離れになる前より、そう思う気持ちがさらに強くなった。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あなたが私の妹じゃないって言ってるんじゃないわ。\nでもその身体は……Aroma一人だけのものではないでしょう？\nそのことを意識すればするほど、どうすればいいのか分からなくなるのよ……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "私、分かる。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "私も同じだから……\n家を出てから、自分の物じゃない記憶がどんどん鮮明になっていったの……\n最初はもやがかかったみたいに朧気で、すごく遠くに感じたのに……今は……さっきの夢ですら、まるで昨日起きたことのようにはっきりと思い出すことができる。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……そうだったの……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "私……もう一人の私について知りたい。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……私のやったことは正しかったみたいね。\nよかっ……た……あら？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "はは……私、泣いてるの？\nホッとしたのに……なのになんで……こんなに悲しいの……\n……うぅ……っ……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ずっとね……分かってたの……\n本当のあなたは……あの夜いなくなってしまったんだって……\nでも、それを認めてしまったら、あなたに対してどんな気持ちで、何者として接したらいいのか分からなくなってしまう気がして……\nあなたの口から発せられる「お姉ちゃん」という言葉すら、まるで知らない言葉みたいで……私……ぅぅ……っ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（Helenaに手をのせる）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃんって呼ばないのは……無理。\nだって、私たちの思い出が、目覚めてから今までの数年が消えたわけじゃないから……\nお姉ちゃんはお姉ちゃんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "この身体にあと何人の自分がいようと、これから私がどこへ行こうと、何が起ころうと……お姉ちゃんが私のことを妹として見ることができなくても……お姉ちゃんはずっと私のお姉ちゃんなの。\n世界で一番大好きな私のお姉ちゃんなんだ。\nだから……お願い、そんなこと言わないで……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "車が止まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "うっ……ぅぅぅ……ぅああ……っ……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma，醒醒。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唔……姊姊？……Asakura 先生的車……？\n……！我們要去哪！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不……不要！要把我帶去實驗室嗎……？你們的對話我聽到了，我不要！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是的！妳冷靜一點！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我原本也不知道自己該怎麼做，不過看到妳這樣的反應……太好了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我現在要把妳送到「JOEZ Cafe」和 NEKO 碰面。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我和她聯絡上了，她也和我說了很多妳離開這陣子的狀況……車也得還給他們才行。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "別那樣叫我。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不……抱歉，我現在情緒有點亂……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我們的對話妳聽到了，那妳應該更好理解了。現在的我……沒有辦法把妳當成單純的妹妹看。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳說話的語氣、神情……和離開前的妳比起來，我又更有這樣的感覺了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "並不是指妳不是我妹妹，而是這副身體……不是屬於 Aroma 一個人的。越是意識到這點，我就越不知道該怎麼辦才好……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我理解的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "因為我也有同樣的感覺……離開你們後，那些不屬於自己的記憶就越來越清晰……起初還只是一些摸不著邊際的模糊畫面，感覺好久遠，但是現在……就連剛剛的夢也好像是昨天才發生的事一樣。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……果然是這樣嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我……想知道另一個自己是誰。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……看來我做的是對的，太好……了……咦？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哈哈……我在哭嗎？明明有鬆了一口氣的感覺，但是為什麼……又覺得好難過……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我一直……都知道……真正的妳那一晚就不在了……但一旦承認了這點，我就不知道該用什麼心情和身份去面對現在的妳……甚至連妳口中的「姊姊」聽起來都好陌生……我……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（搭手）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不要叫妳姊姊，這樣的事……我做不到。我們的回憶，還有醒來後這幾年相處的時光，並沒有消失……妳就是我的姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "無論這副身體裡還有幾個自己，無論接下來我會去哪裡、發生什麼事，無論……妳還有沒有辦法把我看作妹妹……妳永遠都會是我的姊姊，我最愛的姊姊。所以……請不要再這麼說了……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "停車"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗚嗚嗚……嗚啊啊啊……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma......Aroma, 일어나.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "음... 언니? Asakura 씨의 차 안...? 우리 지금 어디로 가는 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "시... 싫어! 날 실험실로 데려가는 거지...? 둘이 하는 얘기 다 들었어! 난 싫어!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "그, 그런 게 아니야! 우선 진정해!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...나도 내가 어떤 선택을 내려야 할지 갈피를 못 잡고 있었는데... 네 그런 반응을 보니.... 결정했어.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": ".......?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "지금 바로 「JOEZ Cafe」에서 NEKO랑 만나게 해줄게.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "어...!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "NEKO에게 연락했었어. 그리고 그 아이한테 네가 실종됐던 기간 동안 무슨 일이 있었는지 다 들었어... 차도 그 사람들에게 돌려줘야 하니까...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "날 그렇게 부르지 마.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아... 미안해. 나도 지금 마음이 많이 복잡해...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "우리가 하는 얘기를 들었으니 너도 아마 이해하겠지. 지금의 나는... 너를 예전처럼 내 동생으로 단순히 바라볼 수 없는 심정이야.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네 말투... 그리고 표정... 네가 떠나갔을 때 느꼈던 그 감정이 지금은 더욱 커져버렸어.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "네가 내 동생이 아니라는 말을 하려는 게 아니야. 내가 하려는 말은 지금 네 몸... 그건 Aroma 한 사람만의 것이 아니야. 이 사실이 자꾸 뚜렷하게 다가올수록... 앞으로는 이제...어떻게 해야 할지 갈피를 못 잡겠어...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "이해해.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "나도 그런 감정을 느껴본 적 있어... 집을 떠나고 나서 나의 것이 아닌 기억들이 조금씩 선명해졌거든... 처음엔 모든 게 흐릿하게만 느껴졌고 손에 잡히지 않을 만큼 멀리 있는 것 같았는데... 하지만 지금은... 방금 꾼 꿈도 바로 어제 일처럼 느껴져.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...역시... 너도 그랬던 거니...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "난... 또 다른 나 자신이 누군지 알고 싶어...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...내 선택이 옳았어... 정말 다행이야... 어라?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니...?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "하하... 나 지금... 울고 있어? 분명 마음의 짐이 조금 덜어진 느낌인데... 어째서... 이렇게 슬픈 걸까... 흑...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "난 줄곧... 알고 있었어... 진짜 동생은 그날 밤 이미 죽었다는 것을... 하지만 그걸 인정해버리고 나면 그땐 나는 널 어떤 마음으로 대해야 할지 판단이 서질 않았어... 심지어 네가 나를 「언니」라고 불러줄 때도 그 낯선 느낌은... 나는... 흑... 흐흑...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……(손을 꼬옥 잡는다)\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니라고 부르지 말라는 거... 난 못 해. 우리 기억 속에는, 내가 깨어나고 나서부터 몇 년 동안 함께 했던 기억도 자리 잡고 있어... 그리고 그 기억들은 사라지지 않았어... 당신이 바로... 내 언니야.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "이 몸에 몇 명의 기억이 존재하든, 내가 어디를 가든, 다음에 무슨 일이 생기든지 간에... 게다가 나를 동생으로 바라봐 줄 수 없다고 해도.... 언니는 영원히 나의 언니... 내가 제일 사랑하는 언니야. 그러니까... 앞으로 그런 말은 다시 꺼내지 마...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "차를 세운다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "흐....흐윽.... 흐아아아앙....\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma，醒醒。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唔……姊姊？……Asakura 先生的車……？\n……！我們要去哪！？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不……不要！要把我帶去實驗室嗎……？你們的對話我聽到了，我不要！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是的！妳冷靜一點！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我原本也不知道自己該怎麼做，不過看到妳這樣的反應……太好了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我現在要把妳送到「JOEZ Cafe」和 NEKO 碰面。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我和她聯絡上了，她也和我說了很多妳離開這陣子的狀況……車也得還給他們才行。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "別那樣叫我。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不……抱歉，我現在情緒有點亂……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我們的對話妳聽到了，那妳應該更好理解了。現在的我……沒有辦法把妳當成單純的妹妹看。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳說話的語氣、神情……和離開前的妳比起來，我又更有這樣的感覺了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "並不是指妳不是我妹妹，而是這副身體……不是屬於 Aroma 一個人的。越是意識到這點，我就越不知道該怎麼辦才好……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我理解的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "因為我也有同樣的感覺……離開你們後，那些不屬於自己的記憶就越來越清晰……起初還只是一些摸不著邊際的模糊畫面，感覺好久遠，但是現在……就連剛剛的夢也好像是昨天才發生的事一樣。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……果然是這樣嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我……想知道另一個自己是誰。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……看來我做的是對的，太好……了……咦？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哈哈……我在哭嗎？明明有鬆了一口氣的感覺，但是為什麼……又覺得好難過……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我一直……都知道……真正的妳那一晚就不在了……但一旦承認了這點，我就不知道該用什麼心情和身份去面對現在的妳……甚至連妳口中的「姊姊」聽起來都好陌生……我……嗚嗚……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（搭手）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不要叫妳姊姊，這樣的事……我做不到。我們的回憶，還有醒來後這幾年相處的時光，並沒有消失……妳就是我的姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "無論這副身體裡還有幾個自己，無論接下來我會去哪裡、發生什麼事，無論……妳還有沒有辦法把我看作妹妹……妳永遠都會是我的姊姊，我最愛的姊姊。所以……請不要再這麼說了……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "停車"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "嗚嗚嗚……嗚啊啊啊……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Car_Moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma……Aroma，醒醒。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唔……姊姊？ ……Asakura 先生的车……？\n……！我们要去哪！ ？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不……不要！要把我带去实验室吗……？你们的对话我听到了，我不要！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是的！妳冷静一点！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我原本也不知道自己该怎么做，不过看到妳这样的反应……太好了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我现在要把妳送到「JOEZ Cafe」和 NEKO 碰面。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！ ？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我和她联络上了，她也和我说了很多妳离开这阵子的状况……车也得还给他们才行。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "别那样叫我。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不……抱歉，我现在情绪有点乱……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我们的对话妳听到了，那妳应该更好理解了。现在的我……没有办法把妳当成单纯的妹妹看。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "妳說话的语气、神情……和离开前的妳比起来，我又更有这样的感觉了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "并不是指妳不是我妹妹，而是这副身体……不是属于 Aroma 一个人的。越是意识到这点，我就越不知道该怎么办才好……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我理解的。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "因为我也有同样的感觉……离开你们后，那些不属于自己的记忆就越来越清晰……起初还只是一些摸不着边际的模糊画面，感觉好久远，但是现在……就连刚刚的梦也好像是昨天才发生的事一样。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……果然是这样吗……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我……想知道另一个自己是谁。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……看来我做的是对的，太好……了……咦？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "哈哈……我在哭吗？明明有松了一口气的感觉，但是为什么……又觉得好难过……呜……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我一直……都知道……真正的妳那一晚就不在了……但一旦承认了这点，我就不知道该用什么心情和身份去面对现在的妳……甚至连妳口中的「姊姊」听起来都好陌生……我……呜呜……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……（搭手）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不要叫妳姊姊，这样的事……我做不到。我们的回忆，还有醒来后这几年相处的时光，并没有消失……妳就是我的姊姊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "无论这副身体里还有几个自己，无论接下来我会去哪里、发生什么事，无论……妳还有没有办法把我看作妹妹……妳永远都会是我的姊姊，我最爱的姊姊。所以……请不要再这么说了……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "停车"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "呜呜呜……呜啊啊啊……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos5101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}